Name: Food Stranding
About the game: An incredibly dynamic and exciting game for a food delivery man against a maddened crowd of customers, shoot enemies every second, move and Dodge, throw explosive tomatoes, buy upgrades and hold out until the very end! Food Stranding-2d shooter with platforming elements, shoot waves of enemies, change weapons, buy new ones, shoot boxes with bonuses, each wave presents new difficulties. Features of the game: - Hardcore - Music - Beautiful Pixel-Art
